@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Run Task
POST {{baseUrl}}/run-task
Content-Type: application/json

< ./payloads/run-task.json

### Compare Models
POST {{baseUrl}}/compare
Content-Type: application/json

< ./payloads/compare.json

### Leaderboard Prompt Mode
POST {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard
Content-Type: application/json

< ./payloads/leaderboard-prompt.json

### Leaderboard Historical Mode
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard?page=1&page_size=10&sort_strategy=balanced&aggregation=latest

### Leaderboard Historical Mode (Filtered Models)
GET {{baseUrl}}/leaderboard?page=1&page_size=10&sort_strategy=balanced&aggregation=latest&models=small,quality
